commit.message:
Helm chart: ensure that identifier is set explicitly
Added note to README about unique owner identity
example and doc update for provider includes/excludes by DNS zone ids
Updated README.md for Azure provisioning controller
change signature of target extractor + rearrange rescheduling

Initial contribution of external-dns-management

This commit contains a first version of:
- The API Group objects for DNSEntry and DNSProvider
- A library that can be used to implement DNS Source Controllers
- A library that can be used to implement DNS Provisioning Controllers
- Source controllers for Services and Ingresses based on annotations.
- Provisioning Controllers for Amazon Route53 and Google CloudDNS.
- A controller manager hosting all these controllers.

Find details in the README.md.
